.com/resizer/v2/QE56BAUABJAQVAQ3ZNNKPBCF7Q.jpg?auth=6e4737000b8e5c678cafe53c65034a66f3d6652afb7dc56cb809f375cb2e9ba1&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F12-06-2025%2Ft_9297a2dc605140c198d75e7f95c38d28_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=723246c411cc01d140fef071ff52d9b6914a6c536ee76e747669a7a6b870257f&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F12-06-2025%2Ft_af2874d77d004d2db1caec16147e99a4_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=c47f3b81ed06236314d4f49680a14c98e2b50cec61a275d6e3b1b3b3b6c8cc03&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F12-06-2025%2Ft_ecdaaecf6bd3481eb93b91a0a44a6a8e_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=5b265c00cf6908afee35fffdd82b9eb6c29f52474d31cef226730e1c10f02e9b&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F12-06-2025%2Ft_b66680502734445ba690353b3eba0842_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=55d1fdb3ea2c45321e9c006ea1892639c9f9508831eea015c09c0398428797a4&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/LXCDSG3NXRHYHBOECKAFRMOXV4.png?auth=7dd2ab2baa67b1e7f2f094ff2dbb10f9cb0a55d7f8a3410cd2fb2c5202390693&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/YWZCJID5TJBRNG4RGLEORD2M6M.png?auth=b24d17cc9b108b1387df84a294ec8d1003b1f8e4bf8aa95f3319e645743aadc0&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F12-05-2025%2Ft_c2bc38e19511438ba698152cc5323498_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=6adf193f78c39e30903b8f75c3af3aa794b2995a581345b355e7558bb72b5011&width=800&height=450&smart=true"], "publication-date": "2024-07-11", "text": "BRYAN, Texas (KBTX) - Bryan and College Station law enforcement officers are participating in the annual Tip-a-Cop fundraiser.\n\nThe event raises money for the Special Olympics and its athletes. Tip-a-Cop will be held from July 22 through 25 from 3 p.m. to 10 p.m.\n\nThe 4-day fundraiser will see officers from multiple local agencies assisting wait staff for tips at the Texas Roadhouse - located at 1601 University Drive East.\n\nThe fundraising goal is $50,000.\n\nNationally, Tip-A-Cop is held only on July 25, however Lieutenant Jason James of the Bryan Police Department (BPD) said they stretched out the event because of its popularity.\n\n“We have so many officers who want to participate, so much of the community want to come out to support the officers and the athletes,” Lt. James said.\n\nLt. James also said this is an opportunity for law enforcement to interact with the community, and for the public to get to know the Brazos Valley officers.\n\n“We just go out and have fun, and interact with the community,” added Lt. James. “This is a good time to talk to the officers, get to know the officers that patrol your area.”\n\nAcceptable donations include cash, checks, and credit card donations. For more information, check out theirFacebookpage.\n\nIf you are unable to make Tip-a-Cop and would like to make a monetary donation to the Special Olympics, you can goonlineor mail a donation to:\n\nBryan Police Department Lt. Jason James 303 East 29th Street Bryan, Texas 77803 979-209-5322 Checks payable to “Special Olympics Texas.”\n\nCopyright 2024 KBTX. All rights reserved.", "title": "Bryan, College Station officers participate in annual fundraiser benefitting Special Olympics", "top-image": "https://gray-kbtx-prod.gtv-cdn.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Fdo0bihdskp9dy.cloudfront.net%2F07-11-2024%2Ft_563b5d3b257a40c5a0425acb57ab18b2_name_file_1280x720_2000_v3_1_.jpg?auth=1867b6530317a95ac758acce271d5452c218203fbbd20e6eae999f0404d276a0&width=800&height=450&smart=true", "domain": "www.kbtx.com", "lang": "en", "author": "", "description": "Local law enforcement officers are participating in the annual Tip-A-Cop fundraiser. ", "keywords": ""}